Package ch.zhaw.it.pm3.spacerunner.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ShopContentCellControllerListener
    The ShopContentCellControllerListener is used to depict the updated coin-value in ShopViewController, when a shop content was purchased in ShopContentCellController by pressing the buy-Button.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FXMLImageProxy
    Image proxy for FXML-Images.
    GameEndedViewController
    Displays achievements of a game and redirects the user to his/her next desired view.
    GameViewController
    Visual appearance of the game.
    HelpViewController
    Displays description of game functionality.
    MenuViewController
    Visual entry point of program.
    SettingsViewController
    Processes user input and persists the adjustments of the profile.
    ShopContentCellController
    Shop-view (Shop.fxml) has multiple ShopContentCells.
    ShopViewController
    The ShopViewController is a controller-class, which is responsible for the shop-view (Shop.fxml).
    ViewController
    Defines required methods of a ViewController and stores the achievements of the last played game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FXMLFile
    Enumeration of the FXML-files that are being used, containing the file path to the FXML.
